org.forgerock.openidm.provisioner.openicf

Class ConnectorReference

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openidm.provisioner.openicf.ConnectorReference

  • public final class ConnectorReference
extends Object
    ConnectorReference holds the required value to find the correct connector in the ConnectorInfoManager. The getConnectorHost is the key for the ConnectorInfoManager newBuilder.
    Version:
    $Revision$ $Date$
